OL,3,CFormer Tory chairman Sir Jake Berry
OL,4,Cjoins Reform UK
OL,6,FFormer Conservative chairman Sir Jake
OL,7,FBerry has announced that he has
OL,8,Fdefected to Reform UK - in the latest
OL,9,Fmove by a senior Tory to Nigel
OL,10,FFarage's party.
OL,12,FSir Jake, who served in Liz Truss'
OL,13,Fshort-lived government, said his
OL,14,Fformer party had "lost their way" as
OL,15,Fhe left the Conservatives.
OL,17,FSpeaking to the Sun newspaper, the new
OL,18,FReform member added: "Old Westminster
OL,19,Fpolitics has failed.
