OL,6,FBefore serving in Ms Truss's
OL,7,Fgovernment, he was a minister during
OL,8,Fboth Boris Johnson and Theresa May's
OL,9,Fpremierships, with responsibilities
OL,10,Ffocused on the Northern Powerhouse and
OL,11,Flevelling up.
OL,13,FIn a video published alongside the
OL,14,FSun's reporting, Sir Jake spoke of his
OL,15,Ftime in government.
OL,17,FAfter claiming that "Britain is
OL,18,Fbroken", he added: "I know who broke
OL,19,Fit because I was there.
