OL,3,CFormer Tory chairman Sir Jake Berry
OL,4,Cjoins Reform UK
OL,6,F"For 30 years I supported the
OL,7,FConservative Party, for 14 years I was
OL,8,Fone of their MPs, sitting at that
OL,9,FCabinet table twice.
OL,11,F"I want to tell you today my friends
OL,12,Fthat I have come to a decision. The
OL,13,Fold parties do not have what it takes
OL,14,Fto transform our country, to build a
OL,15,FBritain we can believe in again, and
OL,16,Fthat's why I've decided to join the
OL,17,FReform Party."
